I"<p>Hunter has been an absolute titan and powerhouse in the EDM industry for many years. An original co-creator of the insanely successful blogs and networks <a href="https://runthetrap.com">RUN THE TRAP</a> and <a href="https://soundcloud.com/toofutureshop">Too Future</a>, he has also been instrumental in building and supporting the growing careers of artists like <a href="https://whoskid.com">K?D</a>, <a href="https://leaveyourautograf.com">Autograf</a> and <a href="https://medasinmusic.com">Medasin</a> through his management agency and record label, ALT:VISION, which recently partnered with major label Republic/Casablanca.</p>

